###Admin login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"admin1@gmail.com",
    "password":"ad1@1234"
}

###Read all users and authors (email)
GET http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users


###Block or active user and author
PATCH  http://localhost:4000/admin-api/user

{
    "email":"admin@email.com",
    "isUserActive":"false"
}